text: Ernest M端hlen (8 June 1926 - 19 March 2014) was a Luxembourgish politician for the Christian Social People's Party, economist, and financial journalist. In 1973, he won a place on Luxembourg City's communal council. He was born in Ettelbruck. M端hlen died on 19 March 2014 at the age of 87. ==References== ==Other websites== * Ernest M端hlen at the European Parliament website Category:1926 births Category:2014 deaths Category:Economists Category:Government ministers of Luxembourg Category:Journalists
